 Without draining the pot, transfer the noodles directly into four
 serving bowls. To the boiling water, add the spinach and
 mushrooms and cook for 1 minute. Drain the vegetables and divide
 evenly among the four bowls.
 Ladle the soup broth into the bowls, top with the cooked beef, sh
 cakes and scallions.
