 cubed
 4 cups (960 ml) low-sodium chicken broth
 2 bay leaves
 3 tbsp (12 g) chopped fresh parsley
 ⅛ tsp crushed red pepper akes
 Kosher salt and black pepper
 4 tbsp (56 g) butter
 4 tbsp (32 g) all-purpose our
 2½ cups (600 ml) 2-percent or whole milk
